As shown in Fig. 12
                        a, some Cr was adsorbed on the surface of the reacted ZBA photocatalyst. Fig. 12b showed that the binding energy of Cr2P was consistent with that of Cr (III) in Cr (OH)3, confirming the reduction process of Cr (VI) to Cr (III) under visible light [42,43] (Fig. 13
